{"tid":478613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加州痴漢秘製精液蜂蜜　女同事飲足兩個月","createTime":"2017-11-24T08:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T12:49:48.000Z","uid":72009,"like":111,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"d1360049f90a989b8c39610c3e420dc78c21ef14","tid":478613,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T08:55:50.000Z","msg":"美國加州洛杉磯一名變態痴漢，涉嫌在由去年至今年初期間，於辦公室內向一名女同事的電腦鍵盤、和滑鼠射精；又拿對方每天吃用的蜜糖罐來自慰，令不知情的女同事慘吃「精液蜂蜜」長達兩個月。 <br />\n<br />\n帕姆代爾市的米蘭卡斯楚（Stevens Millancastro），在2014年和案中女事主成為同事。米蘭卡斯楚之後多次向女同事的用品射精及自慰。女同事其後發現水杯內有混濁物，故丟掉沒喝，類似情況多次出現，她於是向公司舉報。最終在公司安排下，痴漢的惡行被閉路電視拍下。 <br />\n<br />\n法庭控告米蘭卡斯楚5項罪名，一旦罪成，他將入獄兩年及登記為性罪犯。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171123/photo/bknint-20171123214002890-1123_17011_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171123%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20171123214002890-1123_17011_001_01p.jpg&h=44de025b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99505af8ea9e422b0730e4b3cbaa27e08d1b064","tid":478613,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T08:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6730948e06c1f44e39ba540a8760f2fe44298e","tid":478613,"uid":3189,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T08:57:48.000Z","msg":"咁好營養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90afd8c1d7ee63dfdd736886baac528b5dcdc576","tid":478613,"uid":111571,"like":96,"dislike":1,"score":95,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T08:57:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e451a04ba1ef04d66215bdc5b6a531219d0875da","tid":478613,"uid":64858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T08:57:59.000Z","msg":"